WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.087
How big should each step be?

00:00:02.087 --> 00:00:04.522
That choice is called the learning rate.

00:00:04.522 --> 00:00:06.957
Small steps move slowly but reliably toward

00:00:06.957 --> 00:00:07.652
the target.

00:00:07.652 --> 00:00:10.087
Giant steps overshoot and bounce around, never

00:00:10.087 --> 00:00:10.435
settling.

00:00:10.435 --> 00:00:12.870
So, the learning rate is the key

00:00:12.870 --> 00:00:15.304
dial, small enough to land, big enough

00:00:15.304 --> 00:00:16.000
to move.
